{"tid":811450,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"〖影帝上身〗撞死女童返肇事司機逃逸後折返現場扮成路人：是誰撞的？","createTime":"2018-09-08T20:58:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-08T21:26:05.000Z","uid":179810,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b40fe21c1289ced2c692c2445321026ff1aac25a","tid":811450,"uid":179810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T20:58:42.000Z","msg":"笑撚死<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20180908/photo/bkn-20180908081626527-0908_00952_001_01p.jpg?20180908081827\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20180908%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180908081626527-0908_00952_001_01p.jpg%3F20180908081827&h=e461ee92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n貴州貴陽市雲岩區一名1歲半女童，周四（6日）上午在所住屋苑的停車場內，被一輛私家車撞倒，送往醫院搶救無效死亡。有指肇事司機在逃逸後折返現場，更扮成路人查問。當地警方透露，目前肇事司機已經自首，事故原因仍有待進一步調查。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n屋苑居民稱，事發於周四上午8時10分左右，當時女童的母親抱着被撞倒後的孩子向旁人求助，「太可怕了，我當時看到那個媽媽抱起滿身是血的娃娃都在發抖」；而不幸被撞死的女童，據說是家中好不容易才誕下的「二胎」。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n另有居民表示，事發時肇事司機將停在車位的私家車開出之際，女童跑出被撞倒，私家車後輪壓在她的頭上，而司機未有即時停下，反而驅車停在屋苑範圍內的一家超市外，「隨後司機回到現場，手中夾一個包，假裝在那兒問是誰撞的」。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n居民透露，事發停車場進出的車輛大多數是屋苑業主的車和的士，「一般這個路段行人比較少，那些車都開得很快」；居民又指，事發路段的閉路電視形同虛設，有等於無。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20180908/photo/bkn-20180908081626527-0908_00952_001_02b.jpg?20180908081827\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20180908%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180908081626527-0908_00952_001_02b.jpg%3F20180908081827&h=509b121f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20180908/photo/bkn-20180908081626527-0908_00952_001_03b.jpg?20180908081827\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20180908%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180908081626527-0908_00952_001_03b.jpg%3F20180908081827&h=d1be7738&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"39346172a1cf8713f9baf9f72c82db8e428cd43a","tid":811450,"uid":16567,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T21:02:02.000Z","msg":"就咁由得個歲零嘅靚妹係停車場跑？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91df029318a8410bf1d94024edf167844ee85f01","tid":811450,"uid":43314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"39346172a1cf8713f9baf9f72c82db8e428cd43a","tid":811450,"uid":16567,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T21:02:02.000Z","msg":"就咁由得個歲零嘅靚妹係停車場跑？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T21:07:40.000Z","msg":"大陸啲細路淨係識跑車行嘅路"},{"pid":"a6793f8eecb78fa8bd8a14b4b8846c9cb94e5418","tid":811450,"uid":141164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T21:10:06.000Z","msg":"頭都壓爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a827dfad3b5be3caf1fcdab1e05c64b907387ae9","tid":811450,"uid":66527,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"39346172a1cf8713f9baf9f72c82db8e428cd43a","tid":811450,"uid":16567,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T21:02:02.000Z","msg":"就咁由得個歲零嘅靚妹係停車場跑？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T21:26:05.000Z","msg":"大陸人唔識照顧同教仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}